    "Traditional linear modelling approaches may fall short in capturing the complexity of these systems.",
    "Embracing dynamic modelling techniques, such as agent-based models and system dynamics, can provide a more accurate representation of the interactions between ecological processes and climate dynamics.",
    "Policy implicationsAccurate ecological and climate monitoring data directly influence policy decisions aimed at mitigating climate change impacts and preserving biodiversity.",
